tx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Sports+Illustrated&amp;rft.atitle=Lost+In+History&amp;rft.date=1996-08-19&amp;rft.aulast=Mann&amp;rft.aufirst=Jack&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.si.com%2Fvault%2F1996%2F08%2F19%2F216207%2Flost-in-history-from-1929-to-1931-the-philadelphia-as-were-the-best-team-in-baseball-with-four-future-hall-of-famers-and-a-lineup-that-dominated-babe-ruths-legendary-yankees-so-why-hasnt-anyone-heard-of-them&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APhiladelphia+Athletics" class="Z3988"></span></span>
